# Key UI Patterns Quick Reference

Common reusable structures. See `src/app/page.tsx` for detailed HTML structure and `src/app/globals.css` for associated CSS classes.

## 1. Hero Section
-   Layout: Multi-column on desktop, stacks on mobile.
-   Content: Prominent H1, supporting text, CTA, visual element (e.g., animated card).

## 2. Feature/Service Cards (`.feature-card`)
-   Style: `bg-white`, padding, rounded corners, border, hover effects.
-   Content: Typically icon, title, description.

## 3. Pricing Card (using `.card`)
-   Layout: Often a single, prominent card.
-   Content: Plan info, price, features list, CTA.

## 4. Testimonial Cards (using `.card`)
-   Content: Quote, name, title.

## 5. FAQ Items (`.faq-item`)
-   Style: Question (bold/larger), answer, bottom border.
    *No interactive accordion implemented yet.*

## 6. Badges (`.badge`)
-   Style: Small, rounded, accent-colored background/text for highlights.

